MVP
User friendly Home page where visitors can enter a need.
Submitted need will render onto a Needs page.
User can respond to needs by selecting the boxes they want on Needs page.
Once the item is selected, that person offering to fill the need can send the needer an email alert.
The needer and offerer will connect on their own.
  
Stretch
A dropdown on Home page to categorize the need when making a submission.
A counter to limit the number of offers when making a submission. 
Categorization on the needs on the Needs page that breaks the needs into categories.
Remove need from Needs page when the need is fulfilled or the counter is reached. 
